HEADWORD: Phloëm
<hw>Phlo"⟦eum⟧m</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
bark.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>That portion of fibrovascular
